No. 10-6616. Troy Anthony Francis Gordon, Petitioner v. Eric H. Holder, Jr., Attorney General. 562 U.S. 1054, 131 S. Ct. 610,

178 L. Ed. 2d 453,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 8935. November 15, 2010.
